{"tid":1789783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個錯過嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T12:58:07.000Z","uid":279124,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef2fd08c8f21ceb49d7572e5f55c33339bdb713","tid":1789783,"uid":279124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n前排打算買個袋，本身嫌貴冇買，隔一排見佢特價又想諗多一日先決定買唔買，點知隔咗一日之後個優惠冇咗，隔多兩日，個袋賣曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實感情都係一樣，有時遇到心頭好就行動喇，有些人一旦錯過就不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f149d262836ce6b3529fe032b106d27d847fad0b","tid":1789783,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"Twitter組不斷搵緊關於星火tweets入<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">task1</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家除左<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">rt + like + reply</span></span> 之外<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=2885565f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n可以去task1入面美國參議員講香港的tweets Reply講星火被凍結資產的事件<br />\n<br />\n記住twitter一定要用reply ，令外國議員見到香港最新狀況/外國媒體報導，先係衝到出國際，如果只係香港人出tweet，大家香港人不斷rt, 都剩係停留響同溫層本地圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a>"},{"pid":"553a701295e60580a7b5be7b8b065d132cc4e2bb","tid":1789783,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h